
Short Description:
The Naas plugin for moodle allows teachers to add an Aerospace Digital Nugget (ADN) to a course. The students can then visualize the interactive nugget content on the moodle page.

Long Description:
The Naas plugin for moodle allows teachers to add an Aerospace Digital Nugget (ADN) to a course. The teacher can choose an ADN from a large list of contents. Some ADN are public and opened to all schools, others depend on the school credentials of the NaaS. An ADN can be selected by a single click, another click will unselect the ADN.

The ADN is imported in the moodle course with this plugin. The students can directly interact with the learning content.
